{"tid":519492,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔成日話窮人唔好生仔","createTime":"2018-01-04T11:57:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-04T23:07:58.000Z","uid":149978,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"05ff5ba6c300a010048a7f9c64c39b0d6ffc1a25","tid":519492,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T11:57:31.000Z","msg":"不如叫班窮撚唔好媾女，話窮人媾女正仆街<br />\n<br />\n媾女結果通常都會發展成咁<br />\n<br />\n1. 媾女 &gt; 拍拖 &gt; 結婚 &gt; 做愛 &gt; 中出 &gt; 有左bb &gt; 生仔生女<br />\n<br />\n2. 媾女 &gt; 拍拖 &gt; 做愛 &gt; 中出 &gt; 有左bb &gt; 奉子成婚 &gt; 生仔生女 <br />\n<br />\n窮撚都去打飛機，享受打飛機的自由自在，唔駛去媾女，就唔會有窮人生仔。<br />\n<br />\n有些post仲叫埋人戒J搵女，戒打飛機多做愛，掛唔得地球有咁多窮人生仔啦。"},{"pid":"6d0b29b785da747f06d8b01c748cd6cc47b8979b","tid":519492,"uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T12:05:47.000Z","msg":"連登仔成日講到A0毒撚好慘，<br />\n又恥笑無女的A0毒撚，<br />\n呢些咪間接鼓勵更多窮人生仔生女的行為lor。<br />\n<br />\n不如講下做A0毒撚的好處啦。<br />\n例如唔駛駛錢，自由等。"},{"pid":"87e3dad995667c7f19bfa3d4d7ebaa3dedf75c1b","tid":519492,"uid":22302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T18:39:45.000Z","msg":"做愛&gt;中出<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a62f6db9fcb3676aef95acb742893c935bbb916","tid":519492,"uid":44073,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T19:15:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7f200ef09ce7f45ffe45e2c6ab3bdb2776222eb7","tid":519492,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T23:07:58.000Z","msg":"窮撚絕育計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}